      <title>Meta 因分享 WhatsApp 数据被尼日利亚罚款 2.2 亿美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/nigeria-s-antitrust-agency-slaps-meta-with-220-million-fine</link>
