    <item>
      <title>CrowdStrike 崩溃导致受影响的计算机手动重启</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-gaffe-forces-manual-reboot-of-computers-around-world</link>
      <description><![CDATA[造成此次网络故障的网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 在周五的一份声明中表示，周五发生的全球 IT 故障导致所有受其影响的 Windows 计算机都需要手动重启。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/crowdstrike-gaffe-forces-manual-reboot-of-computers-around-world</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 15:19:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>全球 IT 故障让网络公司 CrowdStrike 备受关注</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-collapse-puts-cyber-firm-crowdstrike-in-spotlight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[导致航班停飞、市场混乱、全球企业陷入瘫痪的大规模 IT 故障的背后是一家网络安全公司：CrowdStrike Holdings Inc.]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-it-collapse-puts-cyber-firm-crowdstrike-in-spotlight</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 12:18:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>航空公司在停运后恢复航班，旅行混乱加剧</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，全球范围内的航空软件故障导致航空公司缓慢恢复飞行，数千个航班延误或取消，这种混乱局面预计将持续整个周末。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/global-aviation-grinds-to-halt-as-united-delta-stop-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 08:22:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>从 ATM 到航班，史诗级 IT 崩溃留下毁灭痕迹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周五，网络安全公司 CrowdStrike Holdings Inc. 的一次失败的软件更新导致全球无数 Microsoft Windows 计算机系统崩溃，这将成为全球有史以来最严重的 IT 故障。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-19/microsoft-cloud-service-issues-disrupt-air-travel-operations</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 19 Jul 2024 03:31:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
